# 1. セカイの想いに触れて

Miku: Oh, welcome!
Miku: I didn't realize you were here. Thank you for always watching over everyone.
Miku: The others are here with me today, so why don't we all chat for a bit?
Rin: Hiya! Hehe. I'm so glad you're here♪
Rin: We were actually just talking about everyone's SEKAI!
Len: Yeah! Did you know that they've been changing bit by bit lately?
Luka: Yes, it seems that new areas and little sprouts have been appearing.
MEIKO: Is that because everyone's been growing so much?
KAITO: Probably. They've all experienced quite a lot up to this point.
Miku: Yes, they have.
Miku: Four set out to become professional musicians and have made big strides in their journey...
Miku: Some are working hard as idols each day in order to spread hope to as many people as they can...
Miku: Others overcame a series of walls and obstacles on their way to surpassing that legendary night...
Miku: One group even set out to perform at new and different places in order to make their dreams a reality...
Miku: And some have come face to face with tough facts as they try to find their true selves.
Miku: All of them discovered their true feelings, experienced many things and felt a myriad of different emotions...
Miku: Those thoughts and feelings have begun to change each SEKAI little by little.
Len: Huh? Hey, something over there is twinkling...
Luka: Oh, you're right. Could it be a fragment of somebody's feelings?
KAITO: But it doesn't look like any ordinary fragment...
Miku: Could it be that the SEKAI are trying to tell us something...?
Miku: If so, I'd like to try touching it.
Rin: Me too! I can't wait to find out what sorts of feelings it represents♪
MEIKO: Me neither. Especially if it has something to do with all the others!
Len: Right!
Miku: Would you like to join us?
Miku: Thank you!
Miku: Then, let's go...!
